@startuml
skinparam actorStyle awesome
' --- Visual Styling ---
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFE0B2
    LifeLineBorderColor #2688d4
}

actor Admin
actor Lecturer
participant "Security System" as Auth
participant "Course Management" as CourseMod
participant "Schedule Module" as SchedMod
database "Database" as DB

title Admin & Lecturer Collaborative Flow

== Phase 1: Authorization ==
Admin -> Auth : Assign 'LECTURER' Role to User
Auth -> DB : Update User Permissions
Note right: Admin enables the Lecturer to work

== Phase 2: Content Creation ==
Lecturer -> CourseMod : Create New Course (Java CRUD)
CourseMod -> DB : Save Course Details [1]

== Phase 3: Resource Scheduling ==
Admin -> SchedMod : Define Available Classrooms
Lecturer -> SchedMod : Map Course to Classroom & Time
SchedMod -> DB : Save Final Schedule [1]

Note over Admin, Lecturer : The system is now ready for Student Enrollment
@enduml